===Noun===
'''venerealee'''
#(''obsolete'') One who has a [[venereal disease]].
#:'''Quotations'''
#:*'''1881''': The heavy-lipp'd slave is invited, the venerealee is invited;/There shall be no difference between them and the rest. - Walt Whitman, ''Leaves of Grass''

